title: Abstraction Point 2007 Collection
description:
A collection of MP3s produced by members of the Abstraction Point (http://www.abstractionpoint.net). All files are licensed by Creative Commons, BY-NC-SA 3.0. For up to date information, you might want to check out the AP forums.

Tracks included in this torrent:

Reznyk-
- All Hallows Eve [Ambient]
- Another Day [Trance]
- Crystalline Anomaly [Trance]
- Journey Below [Trance]
- Winter Reverie [Trance]

Null Productions-
- Blackout [Drum &#039;n&#039; Bass]
- BZFrag [Drum &#039;n&#039; Bass]
- BZFrag House Mix [Tech House]
- Ethereal Speed [Speedcore]
- Moonlight Fantasy [Trance]
- Reign of Noize Terror [Speedcore]

WiredTangenT-
- Mercury [Drum &#039;n&#039; Bass]
- Phantom Lights [Drum &#039;n&#039; Bass]

And as an added bonus, we also have included the group project, "Synthesis," created by FotG, Reznyk, and Dexi.

Some tracks have been overlooked in this compilation, but if you really want more, you can find just about everything on the AP forums, at http://forum.abstractionpoint.net. Look for the Beat Exchange board.

Enjoy the tunes, stay tuned for more!
